%2C%20Narela%20and%20Najafgarh%20are%20the%20first%20to%20experience%20the%20full%20force%20of%20these%20hot%20winds%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Srivastava%20said.%20Mungeshpur%20in%20northwest%20Delhi%20is%20the%20place%20where%2052.3%20degrees%20Celsius%20was%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahesh%20Palawat%20from%20Skymet%20Weather%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20open%20areas%20with%20vacant%20land%20experience%20increased%20radiation%2C%20leading%20to%20exceptionally%20high%20temperatures%20due%20to%20direct%20sunlight%20and%20lack%20of%20shade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-ws-url%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fwebstories%2Ffeature%2Fdelhi-among-hottest-places-in-the-world-18122%5C%22%20data-ws-pos%3D%5C%22C%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fwebstories%2Ffeature%2Fdelhi-among-hottest-places-in-the-world-18122%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Iran%20shocker%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extraordinary%20temperature%20at%20Persian%20Gulf%20international%20airport%20was%20termed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FUS_Stormwatch%2Fstatus%2F1680700765265072128%5C%22%3Eunsafe%20for%20human%20survival%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Weather%20experts%20said%20the%20temperature%20reached%2040%20Degrees%20Celsius%20in%20the%20region%2C%20with%20a%20relative%20humidity%20of%2065%20per%20cent%2C%20according%20to%20NOAA%20data.%20This%20created%20an%20apparent%20temperature%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fheat-index-at-iran-airport-hits-66-degrees-celsius-as-climate-scientist-warns-earth-will-become-inferno-4215534%5C%22%3E66.7%20degrees%20Celsius%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExtreme%20heat%20can%20have%20devastating%20impact%20on%20humans.%20According%20to%20vaccine%20alliance%20GAVI%2C%20it%20leads%20to%20dehydration%20and%20if%20a%20person%20doesn't%20drink%20enough%20water%20to%20replace%20that%20lost%20through%20swe