0about%20their%20email%20inbox.%20For%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20an%20unmanageable%20mess%20of%20obligations%20and%20junk%2C%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F04%2F07%2Fopinion%2Fgmail-email-digital-shame.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshame%20closet%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20repository%20for%20a%20decade%20of%20mailing%20lists%20you%20didn't%20realize%20you%20had%20signed%20up%20for.%20For%20some%20people%2C%20their%20inbox%20is%20so%20excruciating%20that%20they've%20just%20given%20up%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeleting-gmail-slack-phone-entrepreneur-parent-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefusing%20to%20even%20check%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20declaring%20email%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20a%20new%20problem.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgmail-20-year-anniversary-launch-memo-announcement-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGmail%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20email%20services%20in%20the%20world%2C%20celebrated%20its%2020th%20birthday%20in%20April.%20When%20Google%20introduced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgmail-inbox%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etabbed%20inbox%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202013%2C%20I%20was%20in%20heaven.%20It%20completely%20solved%20my%20digital%20shame%20closet%20problem%20with%20my%20email.%20The%20tabs%20separated%20important%20emails%20%E2%80%94%20finally!%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0from%20the%20crush%20of%20alerts%20about%20Old%20Navy%20sale%20or%20other%20email%20blasts%20that%20didn't%20require%20my%20immediate%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(I%20would%20note%20here%20that%20if%20you%2C%20personally%2C%20have%20developed%20a%20better%20strategy%20for%20dealing%20with%20your%20inbox%2C%20or%20you%20prefer%20to%20use%20a%20different%20mail%20client%20or%20app%2C%20I'm%20happy%20for%20you.%20Thrilled.%20But%20this%20conversation%20is%20not%20for%20you.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20tabbed%20inbox%20has%20fallen%20behind%2C%20unable%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20ways%20that%20email%20has%20changed%20since%202013.%20Google%20is%20trying%20to%20fix%20it%20(I'll%20get%20to%20that%20in%20a%20second)%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20doing%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226742b53b-69e2-459b-8ea5-f83327e82f04%5C%22%3E2013%3A%20The%20dawn%20of%20the%20tabbed%20inbox%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20launched%2C%20the%20tabbed%20inbox%20was%20designed%20to%20direct%20important%20emails%20to%20your%20%26quot%3BPrimary%26quot%3B%20tab%2C%20and%20send%20others%20to%20Promotions%20or%20Social%20tabs.%20You%20could%20also%20choose%20to%20add%20Forums%20and%20Updates%20tabs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20these%20tabs%20made%20sense.%20People%20still%20received%20%26quot%3BSocial%26quot%3B%20emails%20%E2%80%94%20messages%20from%20Facebook%20about%20new%20birthdays%2C%20anniversaries%2C%20etc.%20But%20in%202024%2C%20who%20is%20still%20opening%20email%20alerts%20from%20Facebook%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20sorting%20no%20longer%20really%20makes%20sense.%20My%20Promotions%20tab%20has%20the%20daily%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Information%20and%20The%20Boston%20Globe%2C%20mixed%20in%20with%20an%20update%20about%20new%20profile%20views%20from%20TikTok%2C%20new%20listings%20on%20Redfin%20(how%20did%20I%20even%20start%20getting%20emails%20from%20that%3F)%2C%20and%20an%20actual%20promotional%20email%20from%20the%20footwear%20brand%20Merrell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screenshot%20of%20my%20email%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f8049239fda2da6cb1465%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22728%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%26quot%3BPromotions%26quot%3B%20tab%20of%20Gmail%20is%20full%20of%20things%20that%20aren't%20promotions.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20apparently%20noticed%20that%20the%20tabbed%20inbox%20isn't%20meeting%20today's%20needs%2C%20and%20will%20soon%20roll%20out%20an%20update%20meant%20to%20alleviate%20the%20burden%20of%20the%20swollen%20Primary%20inbox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289146626-f9ab-4bd4-8bbe-b778e1b70702%5C%22%3EGoogle%20will%20start%20adding%20the%20Updates%20tab%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20will%20add%20the%20Updates%20tab%20to%20all%20user%20inboxes%20by%20default%2C%20and%20direct%20more%20messages%20to%20that%20tab.%20Previously%2C%20the%20Updates%20tab%20was%20only%20an%20extra%20option%20in%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecently%2C%20we%20conducted%20an%20experiment%20that%20activates%20a%20refreshed%20version%20of%20the%20Updates%20inbox%20in%20Gmail%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20from%20Google%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20received%20positive%20feedback%20from%20participants%20and%20are%20now%20bringing%20the%20feature%20to%20additional%20users%20to%20help%20them%20focus%20on%20the%20emails%20that%20matter%20most%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20should%20be%20great%20for%20most%20people%20who%20have%20been%20frustrated%20with%20their%20Primary%20tab%20being%20overloaded.%20Great!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b669dfe1-fd6a-47c5-95de-80ad75ba6f4b%5C%22%3EI%20demand%20a%20Newsletters%20tab%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20still%20isn't%20what%20I%20dream%20of%20getting%20out%20of%20a%20tabbed%20inbox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20dream%20of%20most%20is%20a%20new%20dedicated%20tab%20for%20%26quot%3BNewsletters%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20I've%20subscribed%20to%20lots%20of%20email%20newsletters%20on%20Substack%20as%20well%20as%20regular%20newsy%20newsletters%20from%20publications%20like%20Business%20Insider%2C%20which%20send%20links%20to%20top%20stories%20(by%20the%20way%2C%20I%20highly%20recommend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsi