ns%20inside%20Russia%20%E2%80%94%20but%20on%20one%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacron%20said%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZy8HZETaJT4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20Ukraine%20should%20be%20able%20to%20target%20military%20bases%20in%20Russia%20that%20are%20directly%20used%20to%20launch%20attacks%20on%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20that%20we%20should%20allow%20them%20to%20neutralize%20the%20military%20sites%20from%20which%20the%20missiles%20are%20fired%20and%2C%20basically%2C%20the%20military%20sites%20from%20which%20Ukraine%20is%20attacked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacron%20held%20a%20map%20showing%20military%20bases%20stationed%20inside%20Russia's%20borders%2C%20where%20Russian%20forces%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffierce-russian-attacks-test-ukraine-defense-near-kharkiv-war-expansion-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20launching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-began-kharkiv-offensive-early-trying-beat-ukraine-aid-isw-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffensive%20operations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20can%20see%2C%20Ukrainian%20soil%20is%20being%20attacked%20from%20bases%20in%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20explain%20to%20the%20Ukrainians%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20protect%20these%20towns%20and%20everything%20we%20see%20around%20Kharkiv%20if%20we%20tell%20them%2C%20'you're%20not%20allowed%20to%20reach%20the%20position%20where%20the%20missiles%20are%20fired%20from%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacron%20said%20the%20message%20NATO%20is%20sending%20to%20Ukraine%20right%20now%20is%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20giving%20you%20weapons%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20defend%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20state