20its%20preliminary%20games.%20Kohli%20took%20a%20break%20for%20personal%20work%20after%20RCB's%20IPL%20ouster%20and%20in%20all%20likelihood%2C%20he%20will%20join%20the%20squad%20by%20Friday.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20he%20would%20be%20able%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20only%20warm-up%20game%20against%20Bangladesh%20on%20Saturday%20after%20a%20long%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20played%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20matches%20under%20lights%20in%20the%20scorching%20Indian%20summer%2C%20the%20idea%20would%20be%20to%20adjust%20to%20pleasant%20mornings%20where%20temperatures%20will%20hover%20between%2025%20to%2027%20degree%20celsius%20with%20very%20less%20humidity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20white%20kookaburra%20in%20slightly%20windy%20mornings%20could%20be%20a%20challenge%20and%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20that%2C%20the%20severely%20jet-lagged%20bodies%20need%20to%20get%20used%20to%20morning%20conditions.%20And%20this%20is%20why%20the%20support%20staff%2C%20before%20initiating%20the%20skills%20training%20(net%20sessions)%20on%20the%20practice%20pitches%20at%20a%20ground%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20city%2C%20have%20decided%20to%20help%20the%20players%20acclimatise%20with%20the%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%2014%20players%20checking%20in%2C%20there%20was%20light%20jogging%2C%20routine%20shuttle%20runs%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20foot%20volley%20to%20get%20into%20the%20groove.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20been%20away%20two%20and%20half%20months%20from%20us%20and%20getting%20to%20know%20where%20they%20stand%20and%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20before%20the%20World%20Cup%20is%20the%20goal.%20The%20(first)%20goal%20is%20to%20spend%2045%20minutes%20in%20the%20heat%20to%20get%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20Strength%20and%20Conditioning%20coach%20Soham%20Desai%20told%20bcci.tv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20came%20in%20the%20day%20before%20yesterday%20and%20we%20just%20eased%20into%20our%20routines%20here%2C%20the%20players%20are