or%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iphone-sales-rebound-in-china-april-after-slump-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20woman%20lost%2044%20pounds%20after%20ditching%20fad%20diets%20and%20excessive%20cardio.%20She%20says%202%20simple%20lifestyle%20changes%20helped%20her%20lose%20weight.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223602%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bethany%20Dobson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665709fbf5084fadb175ae1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222702%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBethany%20Dobson%20learned%20how%20to%20make%20lower-calorie%20versions%20of%20her%20favorite%20meals.%3Cp%3EGeorgie%20Glass%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBethany%20Dobson%20ditched%20fad%20diets%20and%20learned%20how%20to%20use%20calorie%20counting%20to%20lose%20weight%20sustainably.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDobson%20lost%2044%20pounds%20by%20making%20lighter%20versions%20of%20her%20favorite%20foods%20and%20eating%20four%20meals%20a%20day.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEating%20a%20fourth%20meal%20in%20the%20afternoon%20can%20help%20you%20feel%20satisfied%20and%20stay%20on%20track%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20women%2C%20Bethany%20Dobson%20grew%20up%20watching%20her%20mother%20and%20grandmother%20go%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffad-diet-red-flags-dangerous-dietitians-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efad%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20fad%20diet.%20For%20a%20long%20time%2C%20she%20thought%20she%20needed%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20wasn't%20until%20Dobson%2C%2022%2C%20from%20Manchester%2C%20UK%2C%20learned%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalories-macros-protein-fat-weight-loss-expert-advice-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalories%2C%20macros%20(protein%2C%20carbs%2C%20and%20fat)%2C%20and%20eating%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20each%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20realized%20fad%20diets%20are%20ineffective%20in%20the%20long%20term%20and%20potentially%20harmful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20put%20these%20lessons%20into%20practice%20and%20made%20two%20lifestyle%20changes%20that%20helped%20her%20lose%2044%20pounds%20over%20a%20few%20months%3A%20making%20lighter%20versions%20of%20her%20favorite%20foods%20and%20eating%20four%20meals%20a%20day%20rather%20than%20three.%20Now%20as%20an%20online%20fat%20loss%20coach%20and%20personal%20trainer%2C%20she%20helps%20others%20lose%20weight%20healthily%20and%20sustainably%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20got%20obsessed%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20could%20eat%20kind%20of%20whatever%20you%20want%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20but%20as%20long%20as%20it's%20macro-friendly%20and%20it's%20obviously%20using%20better%20ingredients%2C%20it%20can%20be%20suitable%20for%20fat%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20Dobson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20weight%20loss%20market%20in%20the%20US%20expected%20to%20reach%20%2493.8%20billion%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20Market%20Data%2C%20Dobson's%20approach%20to%20weight%20loss%20%E2%80%94%20without%20using%20fad%20diet%20plans%20or%20supplements%20%E2%80%94%20goes%20back%20to%20basics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292ad1ee6-b8b1-4c17-b811-2ad48df8a208%5C%22%3EDobson%20started%20making%20lower-calorie%20versions%20of%20her%20favorite%20meals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20Dobson%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20bit%20chubbier%26quot%3B%20than%20other%20kids%20at%20school.%20As%20a%20teen%20she%20thought%20she%20needed%20to%20follow%20restrictive%20diets%20with%20boring%20meals%20and%20do%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwe-need-to-reframe-exercise-and-stop-branding-it-punishment-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcessive%20cardio%20to%20lose%20weight%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20started%20doing%20boot%20camp%20workouts%20and%20running%20even%20though%20she%20didn't%20enjoy%20it.%20When%20she%20was%20around%2017%2C%20she%20started%20partying%2C%20drinking%2C%20and%20eating%20greasy%20take-out%20food%2C%20meaning%20she%20never%20lost%20the%20weight%20she%20wanted%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20changed%20when%20Dobson%20was%20around%2018%20and%20her%20new%20partner%20introduced%20her%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrength-training-women-benefits-lift-weights-celebrity-personal-trainer-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweight%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffat-weight-loss-lessons-wish-knew-younger-age-advice-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20fat%20loss%20methods%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDobson%20went%20from%20believing%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%20foods%20and%20%26quot%3Bbad%26quot%3B%20foods%20that%20cause%20weight%20gain%20to%20learning%20that%20overall%20calorie%20intake%20is%20what%20determines%20whether%20you%20lose%2C%20gain%2C%20or%20maintain%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223602%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bethany%20Dobson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66570a28f5084fadb175ae31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBethany%20Dobson%20used%20to%20think%20eating%20for%20weight%20loss%20meant%20deprivation.%3Cp%3EGeorgie%20Glass%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDobson%20gradually%20started%20partying%20less%20and%20tried%20losing%20fat%20by%20counting%20her%20calories%20while%20eating%20nourishing%20foods%2C%20including%20plenty%20of%20protein%2C%20to%20ensure%20she%20was%20in%20a%20gentle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fcalorie-deficit-diet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalorie%20deficit%20%3C%2Fa%3E(or%20eating%20less%20energy%20than%20you%20burn).%20Protein%20helps%20to%20keep%20you%20feeling%20full%20and%20hold%20on%20to%20muscle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20same%20approach%20recommended%20by%20many%20registered%20dietitians%20who%20have%20spoken%20to%20BI%20about%20healthy%20fat%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20my%20first%20time%20losing%20fat%20without%20it%20being%20a%20diet%20where%20I'm%20starving%20myself%20and%20cutting%20out%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20Dobson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20big%20part%20of%20this%20was%20making%20lighter%20versions%20of%20her%20favorite%20foods%2C%20such%20as%20pasta%2C%20quesadillas%2C%20and%20cookies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDobson%20felt%20strongly%20that%20she%20didn't%20want%20to%20feel%20too%20restricted%20or%20deprived%20when%20losing%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFood%20is%20such%20a%20massive%20part%20of%20my%20life%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20even%20if%20you%20are%20losing%20fat%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20just%20have%20to%20eat%20just%20chicken%20and%20rice%2C%26quot%3B%20Dobson%20said%2C%20describing%20a%20staple%20%26quot%3Bgym%20bro%26quot%3B%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFat%20loss%20isn't%20just%20nutrition%2C%26quot%3B%20Dobson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20always%20like%20to%20tell%20people%2C%20that%20if%20you%20only%20focus%20on%20nutrition%20when%20it%20does%20come%20to%20fat%20loss%2C%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20get%20very%20far%20because%20your%20mindset%20has%20a%20huge%20contribution%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20soon%20realized%20health%20and%20fitness%20was%20her%20passion%20and%20qualified%20as%20a%20personal%20trainer%20and%2C%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20started%20posting%20her%20own%20lower-calorie%2C%20higher-protein%20recipes%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbethanyydobson%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Her%20following%20swiftly%20grew%20(she%20now%20has%20689%2C000%20followers)%20and%20Dobson%20started%20her%20own%20company%20coaching%20others%20on%20fitness%2C%20nutrition%2C%20mindset%2C%20and%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20since%20released%20multiple%20recipe%20e-books%2C%20and%20the%20latest%20is%20out%20on%20June%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20from%20just%20doing%20cardio%20and%20dieting%2C%20to%20actually%20losing%20fat%20in%20the%20right%20way%20and%20actually%20training%20to%20build%20muscle%20properly%2C%26quot%3B%20Dobson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22392fd8e7-84dc-4c4a-9fdd-4b9df5c4c4da%5C%22%3EEating%20four%20meals%20a%20day%20helped%20with%20sticking%20to%20a%20calorie%20deficit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDobson%20also%20started%20eating%20four%20meals%20a%20day%20instead%20of%20three%2C%20which%20actually%20helped%20her%20stick%20to%20her%20calorie%20deficit%2C%20she%20said.%20This%20is%20an%20approach%20Dobson%20recommends%20to%20her%20clients%20because%20it%20can%20help%20keep%20hunger%20at%20bay%20and%20prevent%20them%20from%20reaching%20for%20less%20nutritious%2C%20high-calorie%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223602%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bethany%20Dobson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66570a7785e29ef64829bf85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222702%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENo%20foods%20are%20off-limits.%3Cp%3EGeorgie%20Glass%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20you%20could%20have%20an%20afternoon%20snack%20of%20a%20wholemeal%20wrap%20with%20chicken%20and%20vegetables%20for%20about%20300%20calories%20which%20would%20keep%20you%20full%20and%20satisfied.%20Or%2C%20if%20you%20think%20you%20can't%20eat%20anything%20until%20dinner%2C%20you%20might%20cave%20in%20and%20find%20yourself%20reaching%20for%20cookies%2C%20chips%2C%20and%20candy%2C%20which%20are%20often%20high%20in%20calories%20with%20low%20nutritional%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20brain's%20registering%20that%20you're%20actually%20having%20a%20meal%20rather%20than%20just%20picking%20all%20the%20time%2C%20you%20then%20come%20away%20from%20it%20feeling%20satisfied%2C%26quot%3B%20Dobson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20you%20can%20never%20eat%20less%20nutritious%20foods%20that%20you%20enjoy%20%E2%80%94%20dietitians%20don't%20recommend%20cutting%20out%20foods%20because%20this%20can%20lead%20to%20bingeing%20%E2%80%94%20but%20cutting%20down%20can%20help%20you%20hit%20your%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20choosing%20ingredients%20tactically%20for%20your%20hunger%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Dobson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20has%20worked%20for%20me%20in%20the%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-lost-44-pounds-simple-changes-low-calorie-swaps-meals-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716982622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66570a9185e29ef64829bf8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-lost-44-pounds-simple-changes-low-calorie-swaps-meals-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Everything%20changed%20for%20Bethany%20Dobson%2C%20who%20is%20now%20a%20personal%20trainer%20and%20fat%20loss%20coach%2C%20when%20she%20learned%20how%20to%20lose%20weight%20healthily%20and%20sustainably.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rhosie%40businessinsider.com%20(Rachel%20Hosie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-lost-44-pounds-simple-changes-low-calorie-swaps-meals-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Delhi%20heatwave%20declared%20'severe'%20as%20record-breaking%20temperatures%20cause%20children%20to%20faint%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716982440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fsk