cted-google-promotion-engineer-turned-it-around-tips-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Schools%20Open%20Amid%20Heatwave%2C%20Dozens%20Of%20Students%20Faint%20On%20Campus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMultiple%20cases%20of%20students%20fainting%20and%20feeling%20sick%20at%20school%20were%20reported%20today%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20Bihar%20due%20to%20the%20extreme%20heatwave%20pushing%20up%20daytime%20temperatures%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Opposition%20has%20questioned%20the%20state%20government%20on%20why%20schools%20are%20still%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2016%20girls%20fainted%20at%20a%20government%20school%20in%20Sheikhpura%20district.%20Shockingly%2C%20an%20ambulance%20to%20take%20them%20to%20hospital%20could%20not%20be%20arranged%20in%20time%20and%20they%20were%20taken%20there%20on%20bikes%20and%20e-rickshaws.%20Villagers%20infuriated%20by%20the%20situation%20blocked%20the%20Sheikhpura%20-Sasbahna%20road%20in%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%20Prasad%2C%20headmaster%20of%20Mankaul%20Middle%20School%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20several%20students%20started%20fainting%20in%20class%20after%20assembly.%20%26quot%3BWe%20provided%20them%20with%20water%20and%20electrolytes%20and%20called%20for%20an%20ambulance.%20When%20it%20didn't%20arrive%2C%20we%20used%20private%20vehicles%20to%20take%20them%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20schools%20in%20Bihar%20were%20shut%20for%20summer%20holiday%20from%20April%2015%20to%20May%2015%20and%20have%20now%20reopened.%20The%20eastern%20state%20is%20reeling%20under%20extreme%20heat%20and%20day%20temperatures%20at%2017%20places%20have%20crossed%20the%2042%20degrees%20Celsius%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar's%20Begusarai%2C%20over%20a%20dozen%20students%20of%20Matihani%20middle%20school%20had%20to%20be%20rushed%20to%20hospital%20after%20they%20fainted%20on%20campus.%20Principal%20Chandrakant%20Singh%20said%20they%20have%20arranged%20for%20power%20back-up%20to%20ensure%20that%20fans%20continue%20to%20work%20during%20power%20cuts.%20%26quot%3BBut%20despite%20this%2C%20the%20extreme%20heat%20caused%20the%20girls%20to%20faint.%20We%20gave%20them%20ORS%20and%20then%20rushed%20them%20to%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20scenes%20were%20seen%20at%20Jamui%20district%2C%20where%20students%20at%20several%20schools%20fainted%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20leader%20Chirag%20Paswan%20said%20the%20situation%20is%20serious.%20Stressing%20that%20the%20BJP-JDU%20government%20must%20take%20urgent%20steps%2C%20the%20NDA%20ally%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHeat%20is%20rising.%20Whatever%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20must%20be%20done.%20If%20necessary%2C%20the%20government%20should%20announce%20holidays.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMain%20Opposition%20Rastriya%20Janata%20Dal%20launched%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20over%20the%20situation.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20democracy%20or%20government%20in%20Bihar.%20There%20is%20only%20bureaucracy.%20Why%20is%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20so%20weak%3F%20The%20temperature%20is%2047%20degrees.%20Doctors%20say%20that%20children%20must%20be%20protected%20in%20such%20weather%20conditions.%20And%20here%2C%20schools%20are%20open%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716980760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Flbc0lp28_bihar-schools_625x300_29_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-schools-open-amid-heatwave-dozens-of-students-faint-on-campus-5771585%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Multiple%20cases%20of%20students%20fainting%20and%20feeling%20sick%20at%20school%20were%20reported%20today%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20Bihar%20due%20to%20the%20extreme%20heatwave%20pushing%20up%20daytime%20temperatures%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Opposition%20has%20