22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Flatest-live-news-latest-breaking-news-live-updates-today-latest-news-updates-navy-rafales-nawaz-sharif-pakistan-rajkot-gaming-fire-delhi-hospital-fire-pm-modi-amit-shah-kejriwal-news-today-124052900097_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20melts%20at%2052.3%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20highest%20temperature%20ever%20recorded%20in%20Capital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716979483000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110535103%2Cimgsize-86106.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2F52-3-degrees-celsius-in-delhis-mungeshpur-highest-ever-for-capital%2Farticleshow%2F110535160.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Breaking%20all%20the%20records%2C%20northwest%20Delhi's%20Mungeshpur%20area%20on%20Wednesday%20recorded%20maximum%20temperature%20of%2052.3%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20highest%20ever%20for%20the%20capital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fire%20Officer%2C%20Town%20Planning%20Officer%20Detained%20in%20Rajkot%20Gaming%20Zone%20Tragedy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20action%20in%20the%20Rajkot%20gaming%20zone%20fire%20that%20killed%2027%20people%2C%20including%20nine%20children%2C%20the%20police%20have%20detained%20a%20fire%20officer%20and%20the%20town%20planning%20officer%20for%20questioning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETown%20Planning%20Officer%20MD%20Sagathia%20and%20Fire%20Officer%20BJ%20Theba%2C%20both%20from%20the%20Rajkot%20Municipal%20Corporation%2C%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20Rajkot%20Crime%20Branch%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon.%20The%20officials%20are%20being%20interrogated%20and%20the%20key%20questions%20that%20will%20be%20asked%20of%20them%20are%20how%20the%20TRP%20Gaming%20Zone%2C%20where%20the%20tragedy%20occurred%20on%20Saturday%2C%20was%20operating%20only%20with%20an%20entertainment%20licence%20and%20without%20a%20no-objection%20certificate%2C%20an%20approved%20layout%20plan%2C%20building-use%20certificate%20and%20the%20proper%20fire%20clearances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20owners%20of%20the%20establishment%20-%20Yuvrajsinh%20Solanki%2C%20Rahul%20Rathod%2C%20Dhaval%20Thakkar%20and%20Kiritsinh%20Jadeja%20-%20are%20among%20five%20people%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20and%20a%20fifth%20-%20Prakash%20Hiran%20-%20perished%20in%20the%20fire%2C%20a%20DNA%20test%20had%20revealed%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20manager%2C%20Nitin%20Jain%2C%20is%20also%20in%20police%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20Sections%20304%20(culpable%20homicide)%2C%20308%20(attempt%20to%20commit%20culpable%20homicide)%2C%20337%20(causing%20hurt%20by%20an%20act%20that%20endangers%20the%20life%20or%20personal%20safety%20of%20others)%2C%20338%20(causing%20grievous%20hurt%20to%20a%20person%20by%20doing%20an%20act%20that%20endangers%20their%20life%20or%20personal%20safety)%20and%20114%20(someone%20present%20when%20the%20offence%20is%20committed).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20of%20the%20special%20investigation%20team%20set%20up%20to%20probe%20the%20fire%20said%20that%20the%20team%20has%20been%20given%20the%20go-ahead%20to%20question%20even%20senior%20IAS%20and%20IPS%20officials%20if%20needed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20after%20Gujarat%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Harsh%20Sanghavi%20met%20the%20team%2C%20the%20SIT%20chief%2C%20Subhash%20Trivedi%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20instructed%20to%20probe%20the%20roles%20of%20officers%20associated%20with%20Rajkot%20Municipal%20Corporation%2C%20fire%20department%2C%20police%20and%20power%20utility%20firm%20and%20take%20stern%20action%20if%20they%20are%20found%20guilty.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoS%20Home%20(Sanghavi)%20has%20c