%3B%5BCruise%5D%20is%20like%3A%20'Do%20we%20all%20agree%20that%20this%20is%20what%20a%20camera%20is%3F%20This%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20film%20camera%20and%20a%20digital%20camera%E2%80%A6'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20funniest%20part%20is%20on%20flying.%20It%20was%20like%20he%20put%20together%20this%20entire%20flight%20school.%20So%20he%20would%20literally%20go%20'OK%2C%20this%20is%20what%20a%20plane%20is.%20Here's%20how%20things%20fly.%20Here's%20how%20air%20pressure%20works.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%20during%20their%20friendship%2C%20Cruise%20also%20advised%20Powell%20that%20audiences%20respond%20well%20to%20movies%20that%20tap%20into%20emotions%20and%20stories%20that%20everyone%20can%20relate%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20his%20next%20big%20blockbuster%2C%20%26quot%3BTwisters%2C%26quot%3B%20Powell%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20look%20at%20a%20big%20disaster%20movie%20and%20go%2C%20'Oh%20cool%2C%20the%20world%20loves%20disaster%20movies.'%20No%2C%20no.%20It's%20about%20who%20we%20are%20in%20the%20face%20of%20disaster%2C%20and%20what%20the%20human%20instinct%20is%20in%20reacting%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftom-cruise-glen-powell-top-gun-maverick-prank-helicopter-crash-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716978180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6656ec18d38d94707c2be9c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftom-cruise-glen-powell-top-gun-maverick-prank-helicopter-crash-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Glen%20Powell%20said%20Tom%20Cruise%20flew%20him%20to%20London%20after%20filming%20%26quot%3BTop%20Gun%3A%20Maverick%26quot%3B%20reshoots%2C%20and%20pranked%20him%20by%20pretending%20they%20were%20going%20to%20crash.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ejacobs%40insider.com%20(Eammon%20Jacobs)%2