ve%20Consulting%20and%20the%20Small%20Industries%20Development%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SIDBI)%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20supporting%20women-led%20enterprises%20in%20the%20green%20sector%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%2015%20women%20in%20green%20ventures%20who%20were%20a%20part%20of%20this.%20We%20are%20all%20trying%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20change.%20It%20is%20great%20to%20be%20around%20people%20who%20have%20the%20same%20struggle%20as%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20there%20are%20a%20host%20of%20useful%20online%20courses%20and%20customised%20sessions%20made%20available%20for%20women%20through%20WEP%20and%20its%20program%20partners.%20She%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20put%20us%20in%20paired%20each%20one%20of%20us%20with%20mentors%20who%20help%20us%20foster%20connections%20with%20relevant%20industry%20experts.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20make%20us%20fully%20ready.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20associations%20like%20these%20that%20champion%20the%20revolution%20Upadhyaya%20is%20attempting%20to%20create.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20lies%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20eco-villages%20she%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20creating.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20microcosm%20of%20change%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefined%20as%20%E2%80%9Can%20intentional%2C%20traditional%20or%20urban%20community%20that%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333558%2Fbest-farm-stays-in-india-with-natural-pool-organic-food-slow-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsciously%20designed%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20locally-owned%20participatory%20processes%20in%20all%20four%20dimensions%20of%20sustainability%20(social%2C%20culture%2C%20ecology%20and%20economy)%20to%20regenerate%20social%20and%20natural%20environments%E2%80%9D%2C%20an%20eco-village%20is%20a%20challenging%20concept.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Upadhyaya%20set%20o