lt%20amazing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20audience%20was%20cheering%20Usha%2C%20there%20was%20one%20person%20to%20whom%20the%20victory%20felt%20like%20a%20battle%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20teacher%20who%20went%20beyond%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20March%20through%20May%2C%20Maya%20has%20been%20Usha%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20cheerleader.%20The%20relationship%20was%20reciprocal%2C%20she%20maintains.%20%E2%80%9CUsha%20is%20a%20student%20who%20listens%20carefully%20to%20feedback%20and%20performs%20accordingly.%20This%20willingness%20to%20learn%20helped%20her%20succeed.%E2%80%9D%20While%20many%20factors%20blended%20to%20make%20Usha%E2%80%99s%20win%20a%20reality%2C%20Maya%20recalls%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331610%2Fsma-medication-monisha-hatkar-food-business-startup-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earranging%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20finance%20Usha%E2%80%99s%20trip%20to%20Dubai%2C%20where%20the%20international%20round%20was%20scheduled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20Saiesh%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20mentor%20for%20LegoGoa%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Goa-based%20organisation%20that%20trains%20students%20in%20STEM%20and%20programming%20%E2%80%94%20who%20guided%20me%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20crowdfunding.%20He%20explained%20to%20me%20that%20people%20would%20understand%20our%20cause%20better%20through%20a%20video%20that%20explained%20Usha%E2%80%99s%20family%20background%2C%20her%20interest%20in%20robotics%2C%20her%20dream%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20competition%2C%20and%20the%20financial%20crunch%20being%20the%20obstacle%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frobotics-competition-5-1716469285.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maya%20won%20gold%20in%20the%20senior%20category%20at%20the%20international%20round%20of%20the%20Codeavour%205.0%20AI%20Robo%20City%20Challenge%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frobotics-competition-5-1716469285.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frobotics-competition-5-1716469285-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frobotics-competition-5-1716469285-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frobotics-competition-5-1716469285-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frobotics-competition-5-1716469285-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350950%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUsha%20won%20gold%20in%20the%20senior%20category%20at%20the%20international%20round%20of%20the%20Codeavour%205.0%20AI%20Robo%20City%20Challenge%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Maya%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%2020%20days%20to%20the%20competition%2C%20and%20time%20was%20running%20out.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20the%20video%20was%20a%20good%20idea.%20But%20Usha%20had%20never%20faced%20a%20camera%20before%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20do%20multiple%20retakes.%E2%80%9D%20The%20problem%20was%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20young%20girl%20falling%20ill.%20But%20Maya%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316301%2Fmumbai-prachi-kulkarni-cancer-survivor-story-chemotherapy-surgery-inspiring-journey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20resilience%20to%20achieve%20her%20dream%3C%2Fa%3E%20motivated%20her%20to%20oblige%20with%20all%20the%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20another%20hurdle%20was%20the%20passport%20as%20Usha%20did%20not%20possess%20one.%20%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20Usha%20to%20get%20her%20documents%20to%20the%20school%20the%20next%20day%20so%20we%20could%20begin%20the%20process%20of%20applying%20for%20her%20passport.%20But%20when%20I%20saw%20the%20documents%2C%20the%20details%20were%20erroneous%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maya%20says.%20She%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20school%20entry%2C%20Usha%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20registered%20as%20%E2%80%98Usha%20Kumari%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20her%20birth%20certificate%20data%20did%20not%20match%20this.%20So%20we%20decided%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20corrected%20birth%20certificate.%20But%20we%20were%20met%20with%20a%20setback%20there%20too%20as%20we%20required%20the%20parents%E2%80%99%20marriage%20certificate%20for%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%E2%80%99s%20parents%20did%20not%20have%20a%20marriage%20certificate.%20Procuring%20the%20documents%20from%20the%20village%20of%20Guhala%2C%20Neem%20ka%20Thana%2C%20Sikar%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20the%20parents%20had%20married%2C%20would%20be%20a%20long-drawn%20hassle%2C%20they%20discovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETime%20was%20running%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20conjuring%20a%20marriage%20certificate%20was%20not%20an%20option%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20get%20a%20PAN%20card%20made%20for%20Usha.%20But%20first%2C%20they%20had%20to%20get%20her%20Aadhar%20Card%20corrected.%20This%20process%20along%20with%20getting%20Usha%E2%80%99s%20PAN%20card%2C%20and%20numerous%20visits%20to%20the%20passport%20office%20and%20then%20the%20visa%20office%2C%20occupied%20much%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F227723%2Fcoronavirus-lockdown-teachers-online-classes-delhi-kolkata-chennai-unique-initiatives-inspirational-tan42%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20after-school%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20bargain%2C%20her%20eight-year-old%20son%20Vedang%20%E2%80%94%20who%20had%20also%20aced%20