20platforms%20and%20set%20up%20product%20catalogues.%20I%20expect%20this%20will%20significantly%20boost%20my%20sales%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENidhi%20Bhasin%2C%20CEO%2C%20Nasscom%20Foundation%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20project%20has%20digitally%20upskilled%20900%20rural%20women%20artisans%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Gujarat%2C%20empowering%20them%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20digital%20economy.%20By%20providing%20training%20in%20digital%2C%20financial%2C%20and%20entrepreneurial%20skills%2C%20we%20strive%20to%20create%20a%20lasting%20impact.%20Our%20ongoing%20collaboration%20with%20L%26amp%3BT%20Technology%20Services%20aims%20to%20strengthen%20this%20initiative%20further%20by%20offering%20exclusive%20mentoring%20and%20guidance%20to%20select%20women%20artisans%2C%20with%20a%20vision%20to%20extend%20this%20transformative%20support%20to%20women%20entrepreneurs%20across%20other%20districts%20and%20states.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20objectives%20of%20the%20phase%202%20is%20to%20provide%20handholding%20to%20450%20select%20beneficiaries%20from%20phase%201%20whereas%20150%20handheld%20beneficiaries%20will%20be%20supported%20with%20exclusive%20mentoring%2C%20platform%20onboarding%2C%20and%20network%20enhancement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%2090%20selected%20beneficiaries%20from%20the%20cohort%20will%20also%20be%20provided%20%E2%80%98Access%20to%20Finance%E2%80%99%20in%20collaboration%20with%20financial%20institutions%2C%20ensuring%20that%20rural%20women%20artisans%20can%20thrive%20in%20the%20digital%20economy%20and%20achieve%20long-term%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20nasscom%20foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716469128000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FNasscom-1-1716466922.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wo